snippet.title: Announcing Cuphead: Collector's Edition and Physical Edition!
snippet.description:
The All-Cartoon Wondergame…on your shelf at last!

It’s official: Cuphead is getting both a Physical Retail Edition and a deluxe Collector’s Edition for Nintendo Switch, Xbox One, PlayStation 4, including The Delicious Last Course. More info and pre-order options are available now at cuphead.iam8bit.com!
